{"tid":2448114,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍店提示］WeCare唯家藥房 老闆熱愛大灣區 喺CCTVB 落廣告","createTime":"2021-03-15T16:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T16:04:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5af7f810a5f5d4faa33798d410cc9821ab3155fc","tid":2448114,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"呢位叫做魏戎鈞，佢以前係一個藥房仔，佢立志要開連鎖藥房，一間可以媲美屈臣氏、萬寧嘅藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2fTVxm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2fTVxm.jpg&h=032e0b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年嘅第一年，佢就開咗六間分店，當時佢希望服務本地人，仲要消除大家對連鎖藥房嘅不良印象！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvhnOSx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgvhnOSx.jpg&h=d1983e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二年，係社會動盪、熱血嘅一年，喺呢個危急存亡之秋，佢毅然...放棄咗香港人，返咗去大灣區參加交流團，仲接受橙新聞訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4woyS9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4woyS9.png&h=9c3b553f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三年，佢嫌賣港嘅罪孽仲未深重，再喺tvb賣廣告，藉藉無名嘅佢終於可以同屈臣氏、萬寧睇齊，一齊俾人抵制啦，派嬲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">🚫 WeCare唯家 連鎖藥房 🚫</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/o5nHtvDd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpili.app%2Fpg%2Fo5nHtvDd&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=43374ded\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pili.app/pg/o5nHtvDd</a> /<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongwecare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongwecare&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=36afaec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongwecare</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJpJySM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJpJySM.jpg&h=e8ec2a64&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"ddcbd2fa8b270b0c72487a6a71185b2b658b5b3e","tid":2448114,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:14:59.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n<br />\n80後藥房仔立志開第二間屈臣氏，三年後夢想成真<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2447867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2447867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e1aa0e2b492ac50d8e25f31119527e0621d32f7d","tid":2448114,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:17:08.000Z","msg":"2日上午，「搵錢呢啲嘢，燃點灣區夢」莞港青年創業交流路演會在松山湖舉行。到場的19個香港創業項目負責人，以及其中四位優秀項目負責人進行了項目路演，本次活動由東莞市人力資源與社會保障局松山湖分局、聯合出版（集團）有限公司主辦，雲通科技有限公司、松山湖港澳青年創業基地、松山湖港澳項目轉化服務中心聯合舉辦，橙新聞、東莞市螞蟻智慧網絡科技有限公司承辦，<strong>共青團東莞市委員會指導。<br />\n<br />\n「我們希望吸引更多優秀港澳項目落地東莞，同時推動本土企業家繼續推動技術、管理、業態創新。」共青團東莞市委員會副書記甄禎表示，希望未來繼續積極推進灣區青年創業合作及創新要素融合,探索港澳青年來莞創業新思路,推動青年事業發展。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tuhOMmT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtuhOMmT.jpg&h=7d4ca711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.nfapp.southcn.com/content/201909/02/c2585507.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.nfapp.southcn.com%2Fcontent%2F201909%2F02%2Fc2585507.html&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=8aad271f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.nfapp.southcn.com/content/201909/02/c2585507.html</a>"},{"pid":"c8a6d4b730c1427dc957f522ca7a46e98fbf8802","tid":2448114,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"愛&middot;回家演員又表忠，真係愛国家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2449220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2449220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}